ActiveBuilding,is,a,platform,for,property,management,and,resident,communications,Some,features,included,in,ActiveBuilding,include,maintenance,request,management,and,tracking,package,tracking,and,mass,mailing,to,residents,for,announcements,The,ActiveBuilding,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,ActiveBuilding,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,community,information,managing,package,tracking,information,and,adding,and,editing,content